# Golden snapshots are compared byte-for-byte by tests (ADR-0025). They must stay
# LF on every platform: Windows CI runners default core.autocrlf=true, which would
# otherwise check these out as CRLF and break the byte-exact compare against the
# descriptor renderer's `\n`-only output.
crates/reuben-core/tests/golden/** text eol=lf
